<br />Satisfied.</p></div> <div class='jdgm-rev__pics'>  </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__vids'>   </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__transparency-badge-wrapper'>  <div class='jdgm-rev__transparency-badge' data-badge-type=review_collected_via_store_invitation></div>  </div> </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__actions'> <div class='jdgm-rev__social'></div> <div class='jdgm-rev__votes'></div> </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__reply'>  </div> </div><div class='jdgm-rev jdgm-divider-top' data-verified-buyer='true' data-review-id='b18fd8d5-90f6-408d-8601-dda4cb2d3709' data-review-language='' data-product-title='Mercedes Sprinter OEM Style Half-Slider Window' data-product-url='/products/mercedes-sprinter-oem-style-half-slider-window' data-thumb-up-count='0' data-thumb-down-count='0'> <div class='jdgm-rev__header'>  <div class='jdgm-rev__icon' > K </div>  <span class='jdgm-rev__rating' data-score='5' tabindex='0' aria-label='5 star review' role='img'> <span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span> </span> <span class='jdgm-rev__timestamp jdgm-spinner' data-content='2025-11-18 00:54:47 UTC'></span>    <div class='jdgm-rev__br'></div> <span class='jdgm-rev__buyer-badge-wrapper'> <span class='jdgm-rev__buyer-badge'></span> </span> <span class='jdgm-rev__author-wrapper'> <span class='jdgm-rev__author'>Karl Larsen</span> <span class='jdgm-rev__location' >  </span>  </span> </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__content'>  <div class='jdgm-rev__custom-form'>  </div> <b class='jdgm-rev__title'></b> <div class='jdgm-rev__body'><p>The window is really really nice. Excellent craftsmanship and quality. Slides easily and has stops every inch. The screen is excellent quality as well. I will be ordering another one for the other side. Looking forward to camping in the heat and having cross flow ventilation</p></div> <div class='jdgm-rev__pics'>  </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__vids'>   </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__transparency-badge-wrapper'>  <div class='jdgm-rev__transparency-badge' data-badge-type=review_collected_via_store_invitation></div>  </div> </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__actions'> <div class='jdgm-rev__social'></div> <div class='jdgm-rev__votes'></div> </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__reply'>  </div> </div><div class='jdgm-rev jdgm-divider-top' data-verified-buyer='true' data-review-id='b4b6b0ad-3aee-4e0c-a870-cbd701673670' data-review-language='' data-product-title='Mercedes Sprinter OEM Style Half-Slider Window' data-product-url='/products/mercedes-sprinter-oem-style-half-slider-window' data-thumb-up-count='0' data-thumb-down-count='0'> <div class='jdgm-rev__header'>  <div class='jdgm-rev__icon' > A </div>  <span class='jdgm-rev__rating' data-score='5' tabindex='0' aria-label='5 star review' role='img'> <span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span><span class='jdgm-star jdgm--on'></span> </span> <span class='jdgm-rev__timestamp jdgm-spinner' data-content='2025-10-31 19:10:38 UTC'></span>    <div class='jdgm-rev__br'></div> <span class='jdgm-rev__buyer-badge-wrapper'> <span class='jdgm-rev__buyer-badge'></span> </span> <span class='jdgm-rev__author-wrapper'> <span class='jdgm-rev__author'>Antony Weisstock</span> <span class='jdgm-rev__location' >  </span>  </span> </div> <div class='jdgm-rev__content'>  <div class='jdgm-rev__custom-form'>  </div> <b class='jdgm-rev__title'></b> <div class='jdgm-rev__body'><p>Thank you for providing me with a high quality window.  I am happy with this purchase.</p></div> <div class='jdgm-rev__pics'>  <a class='jdgm-rev__pic-link jdgm--loading' target='_blank' rel='nofollow' href='https://judgeme.imgix.net/tec-vanlife/1761937974__1761937969418-20250719_1312461__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=1024' data-mfp-src='https://judgeme.imgix.net/tec-vanlife/1761937974__1761937969418-20250